@StockBraker The article mentions that there is still a laser in the scheme (2W or 30W).   Also mentions companies &quot;like&quot; $LITE.X and $COHR bring the laser to the $NVDA mix.    Could have just as easily added $AAOI which is full stack and US built.   In a supply-side constraint situation, margins are glorious.   So we may well see another consolidation depending on what contracts are in force. 

