@ElRaydelRiO13 I went into POET knowing its a high risk high reward play. If they can stay true to their word and 1) announce new partnerships and 2) actually start shipping their interposers at scale , the stock can easily 3-4x from here. There is definitely a lot of risk since the tech is new and unproven but holds a lot of promise.

$COHR and $LITE are etablished leaders in LPOs and have most upside

$AXTI is the materials play on optics. Geopolitics risks exist but there is so much demand for InP that COHR, LITE and AAOI need that downside is low at the moment

